  "id": "api/core/APP_ID",
  "title": "APP_ID",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/APP_ID\", \"name\": \"APP_ID\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/application/application_tokens.ts#L43-L45\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"app_id\">APP_ID<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/APP_ID#app_id\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>A <a href=\"guide/glossary#di-token\" title=\"DI token definition\">DI token</a> representing a string ID, used\nprimarily for prefixing application attributes and CSS styles when\n<a href=\"api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\"><code>ViewEncapsulation#Emulated</code></a> is being used.</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID#description\">See more...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a>: <a href=\"api/core/InjectionToken\" class=\"code-anchor\">InjectionToken</a>&#x3C;string>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/APP_ID#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>The token is needed in cases when multiple applications are bootstrapped on a page\n(for example, using <code><a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a></code> calls). In this case, ensure that those applications\nhave different <code><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a></code> value setup. For example:</p>\n<code-example>\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(ComponentA, {\n  providers: [\n    { provide: <a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a>, useValue: 'app-a' },\n    // ... other providers ...\n  ]\n});\n\n<a href=\"api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">bootstrapApplication</a>(ComponentB, {\n  providers: [\n    { provide: <a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a>, useValue: 'app-b' },\n    // ... other providers ...\n  ]\n});\n</code-example>\n<p>By default, when there is only one application bootstrapped, you don't need to provide the\n<code><a href=\"api/core/APP_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">APP_ID</a></code> token (the <code>ng</code> will be used as an app ID).</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/platform-browser/BrowserModule\n - api/platform-browser/testing/BrowserTestingModule\n - guide/deprecations\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/APP_ID#app_id\n - api/core/APP_ID#description\n - api/core/InjectionToken\n - api/core/ViewEncapsulation#Emulated\n - api/platform-browser/bootstrapApplication\n - guide/glossary#di-token\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/application/application_tokens.ts#L43-L45\n-->"
}